    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Katon)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 1</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 2</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 12 | <b>Successes:</b> 1</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 1 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 11</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>This is among the most basic of Katon techniques, often used to light fires when circumstances would otherwise make that difficult. The target takes 1 fire damage, and will catch fire for 1d4 rounds. A successful Reflex save negates both. Objects do not get a save, and will burn until they are completely consumed or until the fire is extinguished.</p>\n\n\n\n",
